 are more secure than others.<br \/>\n<a class=\"blue-btn\" href=\"\/votingequipment\/\">MORE<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<a href=\"\/audits\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-156 size-full\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/post-election-aiudits.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/post-election-aiudits.png 900w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/post-election-aiudits-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/post-election-aiudits-768x352.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/a>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"blue-text\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Post-Election Audits<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Post-election audits provide solid evidence and promote public confidence in election outcomes. Our team advises election officials on conducting post-election audits out in the field and has developed background papers and reports on audits.<br \/>\n<a class=\"blue-btn\" href=\"\/audits\/\">MORE<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<a href=\"\/paperrecords\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-155 size-full\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/paper-records.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/paper-records.png 900w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/paper-records-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/paper-records-768x353.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/a>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"blue-text\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Paper Records<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Election security experts agree that the most resilient voting systems use paper ballots. Learn more about why paper ballots are the foundation of trustworthy elections.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"blue-btn\" href=\"\/paperrecords\/\">MORE<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<a href=\"\/internetvoting\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-152\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/internet-voting.png\" alt=\"internet security\" width=\"900\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/internet-voting.png 900w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/internet-voting-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/internet-voting-768x353.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/a>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"blue-text\">Internet Voting<\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Internet voting endangers voters\u2019 privacy, capacity to vote, and trust that their votes are being recorded and counted accurately \u2014 and erodes public confidence in our elections.<\/span> Read more about the dangers.<br \/>\n<a class=\"blue-btn\" href=\"\/internetvoting\/\">MORE<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<a href=\"\/electionsecurity\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-149\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/election-security.png\" alt=\"election security\" width=\"900\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/election-security.png 900w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/election-security-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/election-security-768x352.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/a>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"blue-text\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Election Security<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Secure elections are resilient: they can withstand and recover from cyberattacks and other threats. The most resilient election systems use voter-verified paper ballots, strong chain-of-custody procedures, post-election audits, and robust recovery plans.<br \/>\n<a class=\"blue-btn\" href=\"\/electionsecurity\/\">MORE<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; el_class=&#8221;support-banner&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;banner-title&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"title-label\">Support<\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"red-text\">Secure<\/span> <span class=\"blue-text\">Elections<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner gap=&#8221;30&#8243;][vc_column_inner el_class=&#8221;right-border&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 class=\"red-text\">Donate to Verified Voting<\/h4>\n<p>A strong and healthy democracy depends on the security of our elections. Join us and help ensure that every vote counts.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"donate-link\" href=\"\/donate\/\">Donate<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 class=\"blue-text\">Join Our Mailing List<\/h4>\n<p>The election landscape is constantly changing and full of complexities. We\u2019ll keep you informed on what\u2019s happening, and what we\u2019re doing to make elections accurate and secure.<\/p>\n<div class=\"wpcf7 no-js\" id=\"wpcf7-f180-o1\" lang=\"en-US\" dir=\"ltr\" data-wpcf7-id=\"180\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"><p role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\"><\/p> <ul><\/ul><\/div>\n<form action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/36#wpcf7-f180-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form init mailchimp-ext-0.5.72\" aria-label=\"Contact form\" novalidate=\"novalidate\" data-status=\"init\">\n<div style=\"display: non